title: WEDNESDAY 3/17 - The free agency frenzy continues
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 3/17 - The free agency frenzy continues
description:
the 49ers making a big move to secure their offensive line early this morning (0:08). The Bears land a QB (0:27), but not the one many were expecting. The Lions making some late night moves (0:48), while The Patriots we busy re-building their lineup (1:21). The Jaguars continue to re-tool their roster (1:57), while the Giants lock up Leonard Williams (3:14)...plus, a couple more QBs on the move (3:31)
